sectionText: Meets 13-Mar-17 - 03-May-17. OIIR Dialogue Course. Topic: African/African-American Dialogue. Second half session class. Offered in collaboration with the Office of Inclusion and Intercultural Relations (OIIR)  Go to website http://go.illinois.edu/EPSY203 for more detailed descriptions of the classes. If you still have questions AFTER VIEWING THE WEBSITE, you can email diversityEd@illinois.edu..
